import { Grid, Input, PageHeader, Typography } from 'hero-design';
import React from 'react'
import { useTheme } from 'styled-components';


function Login() {
    const theme = useTheme();

    return (
        <>
            <Grid>
                <Grid.Row style={{ marginBottom: theme.space.medium }}>
                    <Grid.Col span={[16, 16, 16, 16, 16]} offset={[4, 4, 4, 4, 4]}>
                        <PageHeader title="August digital asset management" />
                    </Grid.Col>
                </Grid.Row>

            </Grid>

            <Input
                placeholder="Please enter your user name"
                prefix="user"
                size="large"
            />
            <Input
                placeholder="Please enter your password"
                size="large"
            />
        </>

    )
}

export default Login;
